eg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Building Resilience: 6 Simple Climate Solutions for Big Impact in Nigeria" href="../../../2024/03/15/building-resilience-6-simple-climate-solutions-for-big-impact-in-nigeria5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Building Resilience: 6 Simple Climate Solutions for Big Impact in Nigeria</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Retired Nurse Declares Free Delivery for Pregnant Women in Abia Community" href="../../../2024/03/15/retired-nurse-declares-free-delivery-for-pregnant-women-in-abia-community5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/IMG-20240314-WA0065.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Retired Nurse Declares Free Delivery for Pregnant Women in Abia Community" href="../../../2024/03/15/retired-nurse-declares-free-delivery-for-pregnant-women-in-abia-community5593?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Retired Nurse Declares Free Delivery for Pregnant Women in Abia Community</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Orange Health Medical Centre Champions Health Intervention Programme for Ajegunle Community" href="../../../2024/03/15/orange-health-medical-centre-champions-health-intervention-programme-for-ajegunle-community5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/IMG_20240301_121212_397.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Orange Health Medical Centre Champions Health Intervention Programme for Ajegunle Community" href="../../../2024/03/15/orange-health-medical-centre-champions-health-intervention-programme-for-ajegunle-community5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Orange Health Medical Centre Champions Health Intervention Programme for Ajegunle Community</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="W’Africa Gears Up for Healthcare Innovation Boom" href="../../../2024/03/14/wafrica-gears-up-for-healthcare-innovation-boom5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Healthcare-Innovation-Boom.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="W’Africa Gears Up for Healthcare Innovation Boom" href="../../../2024/03/14/wafrica-gears-up-for-healthcare-innovation-boom5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">W’Africa Gears Up for Healthcare Innovation Boom</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="How to Achieve Efficient Healthcare Ecosystem in Nigeria" href="../../../2024/03/09/how-to-achieve-efficient-healthcare-ecosystem-in-nigeria5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" 